<div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
<p>众资产阶级学者所周知，文革是非常反智的时代，知识越多越反动，谁越无知谁就越光荣，大量有良心的人，有独立思想的人，敢于说真话的人都受到了迫害，人人自危，人人互相举报，灭绝人性。<br>
计算机组成原理断不可能出现在《十万个为什么》里面的。专制独裁的政府实行愚民政策方便其统治。<br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/original/1X/6fd9aab3feaca729941ec19b9ebaa12b751eda3d.png" data-download-href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/6fd9aab3feaca729941ec19b9ebaa12b751eda3d" title="image"><img src="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/6fd9aab3feaca729941ec19b9ebaa12b751eda3d_2_267x500.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="fXtlAvySChNze7Y708BVXZ1cWND" width="267" height="500" srcset="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/6fd9aab3feaca729941ec19b9ebaa12b751eda3d_2_267x500.png, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/6fd9aab3feaca729941ec19b9ebaa12b751eda3d_2_400x750.png 1.5x, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/6fd9aab3feaca729941ec19b9ebaa12b751eda3d_2_534x1000.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/6fd9aab3feaca729941ec19b9ebaa12b751eda3d_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta"><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename">image</span><span class="informations">980×1834 114 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/original/1X/56927c10b062aba8f5035e262ce1f619d84b00a0.png" data-download-href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/56927c10b062aba8f5035e262ce1f619d84b00a0" title="image"><img src="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/56927c10b062aba8f5035e262ce1f619d84b00a0_2_347x500.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="clQU4fdjQqLuoAlEbGPt3fZ2LnO" width="347" height="500" srcset="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/56927c10b062aba8f5035e262ce1f619d84b00a0_2_347x500.png, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/56927c10b062aba8f5035e262ce1f619d84b00a0_2_520x750.png 1.5x, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/56927c10b062aba8f5035e262ce1f619d84b00a0_2_694x1000.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/56927c10b062aba8f5035e262ce1f619d84b00a0_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta"><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename">image</span><span class="informations">997×1435 118 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/original/1X/4ab166e02c3870aa8da64a473870af06db0052ee.png" data-download-href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/4ab166e02c3870aa8da64a473870af06db0052ee" title="image"><img src="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/4ab166e02c3870aa8da64a473870af06db0052ee_2_349x500.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="aELpHuNxLDyBKvG3eEC3xaVsjee" width="349" height="500" srcset="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/4ab166e02c3870aa8da64a473870af06db0052ee_2_349x500.png, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/4ab166e02c3870aa8da64a473870af06db0052ee_2_523x750.png 1.5x, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/4ab166e02c3870aa8da64a473870af06db0052ee_2_698x1000.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/4ab166e02c3870aa8da64a473870af06db0052ee_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta"><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename">image</span><span class="informations">1018×1455 167 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/original/1X/a8b1df9aadacf6604470252bb5edcd49cda73a1c.png" data-download-href="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/a8b1df9aadacf6604470252bb5edcd49cda73a1c" title="image"><img src="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a8b1df9aadacf6604470252bb5edcd49cda73a1c_2_334x500.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="o4lj2H9ne5gMkXm2NGu3s9e9jIM" width="334" height="500" srcset="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a8b1df9aadacf6604470252bb5edcd49cda73a1c_2_334x500.png, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a8b1df9aadacf6604470252bb5edcd49cda73a1c_2_501x750.png 1.5x, https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a8b1df9aadacf6604470252bb5edcd49cda73a1c_2_668x1000.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://mlmmlm.icu/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a8b1df9aadacf6604470252bb5edcd49cda73a1c_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta"><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename">image</span><span class="informations">928×1387 118 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>
